<strong>Interview Archive 4000_0215:</strong> The following is a series of interviews conducted by Dr. Eugene Japers over the course of several years. This data has been expunged from all general documents under Order O5-4000-F26.<br />
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
